><A HREF="gc.htm"> Of God and His Creatures</a><hr><p>

An angel may sin, and may be punished by God: but apparently no 
physical mishap can befall him in the way of accident or disease.  
May not however the state of an angel in sin be described as a guilty 
frenzy?
